Dream Baby Car Reverse Alert Beeper Price: Rs.750

Toddlers are always active and are constantly walking about exploring and trying new things. Sometimes it becomes hard to keep an eye on where they are and what they have crawled into. A dangerous place for your toddler to be is in the driveway and around your car. When your toddler is close to the car when you are about to drive out
column17:
it can put your little one in a lot of danger. The Dreambaby Car Reverse Alert is a useful device that warns your child and other pedestrians that the car is being reversed.

The reverse alert requires no installation and can just be stuck on the back-up (reversing) lights. The device emits a loud beeping noise when the reversing lights come on. The beeper turns off automatically when the reversing lights turn off. The Dreambaby car reverse beeper is a practical device that helps keep your baby boys and girls out of harms way.

Dream Baby Toilet Lock Price: Rs.199

The bathroom is one of the most potentially dangerous places for your curious baby to venture into alone. The only way to keep your baby safe and out of harms way is by baby proofing the bathroom. The first place to start with is the bathroom. The toilet is often at a height that can easily be reached by your baby and that last thing you want is for your baby to open the toilet seat and take a look inside. The Dream Baby Toilet Lock gives you a simple and sure-shot solution to this problem. The toilet lock keeps the toilet securely locked when closed
column13:
preventing your baby from trying to get in.

\r\n

\r\n\tThe adhesive Dream Baby toilet lock can easily be fixed onto the toilet cover. Simply stick the lock on the toilet and clip the latch once it is close. The toilet lock requires no screws for installation
column14: making it an ideal product especially if you are living in a rented house. The Dream Baby Toilet Lock is a useful baby-proofing device that helps keep your baby safe from accidents and safe from nasty germs too. Suitable to use from 3 months of age
